===Transitive verb===
'''to shade'''

# To shield from light.
#: ''The old oak tree shaded the lawn in the heat of the day.''
# To alter slightly.
#: ''You'll need to shade your shot slightly to the left.''
#: ''Most politicians will shade the truth if it helps them.''

